						Learn MoreContact MRC GlobalOperating from more than 400 service locations worldwide, MRC Global has a geographic presence unmatched by its competitors. Our company mandate is simple: Global reach with a local touch. It speaks to the integrity we bring to every project and every relationship, regardless of scale.Global Office DirectoryView MapFirst NameEnter your first nameLast NameEnter your last nameTitleEnter your job titleCompanyEnter your company's namePhoneEnter your phoneEmailEnter a valid email addressEnter your email* All Fields RequiredType Your CountryEnter your countryAddressEnter your street addressCityEnter your cityStateALAKAZARCACOCTDCDEFLGAHIIDILINIAKSKYLAMEMDMAMIMNMSMOMTNENVNHNJNMNYNCNDOHOKORPARISCSDTNTXUTVTVAWAWVWIWYZipEnter your postal codeReason for Inquiry (Optional)SearchInvestor RelationsInvestor RelationsPress ReleasesEvents & PresentationsCorporate GovernanceCorporate LeadershipSEC FilingsStock InformationAnalyst CoverageInformation RequestInvestor ContactsPrintEmailNYSE  : 
			    MRC (Common Stock)
			   $16.18 - 0.59 Data as of 07/21/17 4:00 p.m. ETData provided by Nasdaq. Minimum 15 minutes delayed.MRC Global is the largest global industrial distributor of pipe, valves and fittings (PVF) and related products and services to the energy industry based on sales, and we hold the leading position in our industry across each of the upstream (exploration, production and extraction of underground oil and natural gas), midstream (gathering and transmission of oil and natural gas, natural gas utilities and the storage and distribution of oil and natural gas) and downstream (petrochemical processing, crude oil refining and general industrials) sectors.  We offer more than 230,000 stock keeping units, including an extensive array of PVF, oilfield supply, automation, instrumentation and other general and specialty industry supply products. Through our North American and International segments we serve our more than 19,000+ active customers through over 350+ service locations throughout North America, Europe, Asia and Australia.Annual Reports and Proxy Statements2016 Annual Report2015 Annual Report2014 Annual Report2013 Annual Report2017 Proxy Statement2016 Proxy Statement2015 Proxy Statement2014 Proxy StatementRecent News More  July 17, 2017MRC Global Renews Integrated Supply Agreement with NiSource Inc. July 17, 2017MRC Global Awarded Multiple Nordic Project and MRO Contracts June 07, 2017MRC Global Renews Global PVF Contract with ChevronUpcoming Events More   Friday, August 4, 2017
 10:00 a.m. ETQ2 2017 MRC Global Inc. Earnings Conference Call  Tuesday, August 15, 2017
MRC Global Inc. at Susquehanna Financial Group -  Oilfield Services Conference Location:   New York, NY  Wednesday, August 23, 2017
