Products and Services



Since 1921, we have built our business around sourcing and supplying PVF products. Our value proposition is designed to simplify your supply chain so you can focus on your core business. 






SHARE:  
Print
Email








                            Carbon Steel Pipe
                        



MRC Global maintains one of the largest pipe and tubular inventories in North America. Our carbon steel pipe is available in an extensive range of sizes.

More Information





                            Carbon Steel Fittings & Flanges
                        



MRC Global's carbon steel fittings and flanges are provided from world-class manufacturers offering a strong, long-lasting solution for your needs.

More Information





                            Valves
                        



                                MRC Global represents the leading valve manufacturers in the industry. We work closely with these manufacturers to ensure the highest level of quality and service.
                            

More Information







                            Valve Automation
                        



                                MRC Global represents the premier valve automation lines in the industry. The combination of our global strength and our local, technical service simplifies our customers’ supply chain.
                            

More Information





                            Stainless & Alloy Pipe
                        



                                MRC Global maintains one of the world’s largest pipe inventories and offers our customers the most versatile selections of industrial pipe for corrosive environments.
                            

More Information





                            Stainless & Alloy Fittings & Flanges
                        



MRC Global stocks a versatile selection of stainless and alloy fittings and flanges for corrosive or high temperature applications.

More Information







                            Gas Products
                        



                                MRC Global inventories include products that meet the highest performance and quality specifications, ranging from pipe, meters and valves to couplings, fittings, cathodic protection and more.
                            

More Information





                            Specialty Products
                        



                                MRC Global stocks steam traps, strainers, thermoplastic lined piping products, as well as many other specialty products as part of our extensive, in-stock inventory.
                            

More Information





                            Oilfield Products
                        



                                MRC Global stocks and provides a full range of oilfield products to operators and production crews for well completion to the gathering system.
                            

More Information







                            Mill Supplies & Safety 
                        



                                MRC Global maintains an extensive inventory of general industrial products from first class suppliers.
                            

More Information





                            Measurement
                        



                                MRC Global provides a comprehensive selection of measurement products to customers around the globe. We are proud to be the exclusive provider for this product line in the US and Canada.
                            

More Information





                            ValveWatch®
                        



 ValveWatch is an online monitoring system that utilizes advanced technology to remotely monitor valves and actuators, intentionally detect problems before they impact production.

More Information








