Position： List Of Companies  ›› India ›› MRC GREEN ENERGY SERVICES






MRC GREEN ENERGY SERVICES



Business Type : Manufacturing
Year Established : 2011
Main Markets : Americas,Africa,Asia,America,East Europe,Europe,No
Main Products : Biomass Gasifier,Wood Gas Stove,Power Plant,Thermal .gas Burner, 
Country/Region : India
 Links : India Energy Products, India Other Energy Products, 



Company Introduction

                      WELCOME TO MRC GREEN ENERGY COMPANY India is the sixth largest energy consumer in the world, consuming about 3 per cent of the world&＃039;s total energy per year. Though the annual electricity generation and consumption have nearly doubled since 1990 the country has been facing peak level electricity shortage to the extent of 11-18 percent. Nearly, out of half of a million or so villages in India, about 80, 000 remain completely un-electrified. Thus there is a need for development of long term sustainable solutions so that the non electrified villages have reliable, regular, adequate, or good quality power.                 



