Welcome To EMRC
Energy Market and Regulatory Consultants (EMRC) are consultants and advisers in energy markets, regulation, transactions and commercial issues. We were founded in 2011 as Mercados EMI, and changed our name to EMRC in 2015. We are part of the MRC Group of Companies, a family of seven sister companies, sharing a long and common history of working together. The MRC Group of Companies has a professional team of over 55 trained consultants, with presence in nine different cities.










